## Merge multiple png files using the terminal
   > brew install ImageMagick
   > convert +append a.png b.png merge.png  /* horizontal merge */
   > convert -append a.png b.png merge.png  /* vertical merge */
   > convert -append a*.png      merge.png  /* in case there are multiple files */
   > convert -append a*.pdf      merge.png  /* save as pdf */
